# v0.10.0 note: .acw/ used to mean "runtime cache, never commit." From v0.10.0
# forward (D-ACW-050), .acw/ is canonical substrate (decisions, glossary,
# sessions, etc.) and MUST be tracked. Do NOT re-add `.acw/` to this file.
# Per-instance ephemeral runtime state, if any, belongs at .acw/raw/ where
# it's transient by convention and excluded by .acw/raw/.gitkeep semantics
# rather than a blanket ignore.

# Logs outside the incident ledger
*.log
